      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b>Code of Practice</b></p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>Service charge residential management Code</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>and additional advice to landlords, leaseholders and agents</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>3rd edition</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>Important note</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>The following parts of this document are approved by the Secretary of State under the Approval of Code of Management Practice (Residential Management) (Service Charges) (England) Order 2016.</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>(S.I. 2016/518)</p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p>All parts except ‘RICS guidance notes’.</p>
        </content>
      </level>
